Title: The Elusive Eden
Writer: Joe Gayton (creator), Tony Gayton (creator), Mark Richard, Tom Brady (story editor)
Actors: Anson Mount, Colm Meaney, Christopher Heyerdahl, Robin McLeavy
Plot: Cullen awaits the birth of his baby, laboring under The Swede's thumb at Fort Smith. Durant deals with the fallout from a railroad accident.
